data.description: LOTS of space in this 4/2.5 farm house with wraparound porch, deck and Fenced yard. All new kitchen, new appliances, granite, cabinets, all w/ quiet shut drawers and pull out shelves, huge pantry, built in desk. Freshly painted, new light fixtures and updated baths. Master bedroom has HUGE WIC with built in shelves,vaulted ceilings and ceiling fan.Separate LV/rm, DR/rm and F/rm w/ FP. Home warrant
